Reading is actually first on my personal review of each year, but I wanted to play with the photo collections, so [I started with travel](https://jerrytowler.com/2025/01/04/review-travel.html). I keep an up-to-date list of [books I'm reading and have read](https://jerrytowler.com/reading/), but here's 2024 for posterity, or something.

I hit 21 of my goal of 24, although it's possible one of them ([The Law by Jim Butcher](https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/60653694-the-law)) doesn't show up on micro.blog for some reason, so the below list will only have 20.

